001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.table.insertion;
002
003import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.ComponentType;
004import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium.smart.SmartWebElement;
005
006/**
007 * Defines the contract for inserting values into table cells.
008 *
009 * <p>This interface provides a mechanism to insert data into a table cell dynamically,
010 * leveraging different component types for handling the insertion process.
011 *
012 * <p>Used in {@code TableServiceRegistry} and {@code TableImpl}.
013 *
014 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
015 */
016public interface TableInsertion {
017
018   /**
019    * Inserts values into the specified table cell.
020    *
021    * @param cellElement   The {@link SmartWebElement} representing the target cell.
022    * @param componentType The {@link ComponentType} defining the type of UI component used for insertion.
023    * @param values        The values to be inserted into the cell.
024    */
025   void tableInsertion(SmartWebElement cellElement, ComponentType componentType, String... values);
026}
